Package cz.syntea.xdef.model Description

Provides USER INTERFACE for accessing to XMDefinition objects (models). For In the case you want to know properties of XMdefinition objects of an processed object you can use methods XXNode.getXMDefinition() or XXNode.getXMElement() or XXData.getXMData().

All methods above return an object with properties of processed data. See:
XMNode
XMElement
XMData
XMDefinition
